<IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/profile_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Profile for Jenlei"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://" target=_new><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/homepage.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Author's Homepage"></A> &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/daoc/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=private_message&u=00002054"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/priv_message.gif" BORDER='0' ALT="Send New Private Message"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/daoc/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=edit_post&f=21&t=000971&reply_num=000007&u=00002054"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/edit_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Edit/Delete Post"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/daoc/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply&f=21&t=000971&replyto=000007"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/daoc/quote_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Reply With Quote"></A>
