Again, I reiterate that it *should* seem likely that a Tank will hit the mob harder than your piddly DoT tick and *should* be able to get it off you before you die.  A single mob hasn't been able to kill me in one swipe since I hit 40 or so.  I died once when two trees hit me simultaneously, but that's technically two hits at the same time...<P>So while it can be considered risky, it's also not too wild of a technique if the Tanks are doing their job and putting out damage.
